      "comment": "Great clash with KEAYANG RENEGADE (9) taking on a smart one tonight but he is impossible to knock having stretched his unbeaten run to six by coming from this row to score by close to 8m here last start. He looks the real deal and his fitness edge could prove crucial. SOME AMERICAN (6) is back from a break of eight months but he is a two-time fresh winner who looks to be right up to the mark following two recent trial wins. He is a Group 2 winner with a very consistent record at this circuit and distance so looks a big threat to the top pick's perfect record. KEAYANG WASABI (8) continues to work through his grades and added to a string of top-two finishes when he worked from this row but toughed out a win here last week. ",
